            <table class="custom-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag icon-flag" style="color:#007bff;"></i> <div class="d-inline-block">
                            **شمال أمريكا** <br>
                            <small class="text-muted">Sunday 6:00 p.m. to Friday 11:59 p.m.</small>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="col-4">Chicago</td>
                    <td class="col-4 text-start">**+1 866 344 2088** (Toll Free)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag icon-flag" style="color:#28a745;"></i>
                        <div class="d-inline-block">
                            **جنوب أمريكا** <br>
                            <small class="text-muted">Sunday 9:00 p.m. to Friday 11:59 p.m.</small>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="col-4">São Paulo</td>
                    <td class="col-4 text-start">**+1 31 447 8070**</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-section">
            <h2 class="region-heading">🇪🇺🌍 أوروبا، الشرق الأوسط وأفريقيا</h2>
            <table class="custom-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag-usa icon-flag"></i> <div class="d-inline-block">
                            **المملكة المتحدة** <br>
                            <small class="text-muted">Monday 8:00 a.m. to Friday 11:59 p.m.</small>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="col-4">London</td>
                    <td class="col-4 text-start">**+44 0 186 584 3987**</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag icon-flag" style="color:#ffc107;"></i>
                        <div class="d-inline-block">
                            **هولندا** <br>
                            <small class="text-muted">Monday 8:00 a.m. to Friday 11:59 p.m.</small>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="col-4">Amsterdam</td>
                    <td class="col-4 text-start">**+31 20 485 3767**</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-section">
            <h2 class="region-heading">🌏 آسيا والمحيط الهادئ</h2>
            <table class="custom-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-4">
