                        <div class="d-inline-block">
                            **سنغافورة** <br>
                            <small class="text-muted">Monday 8:00 a.m. to Saturday 11:59 a.m.</small>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="col-4">Singapore</td>
                    <td class="col-4 text-start">**+65 6349 0222**</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag icon-flag" style="color:#007bff;"></i>
                        <div class="d-inline-block">
                            **أستراليا** <br>
                            <small class="text-muted">Monday 8:00 a.m. to Saturday 11:59 a.m.</small>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="col-4">Sydney</td>
                    <td class="col-4 text-start">**+61 1800 572139** (Toll Free)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-flag icon-flag" style="color:#6c757d;"></i>
                        <div class="d-inline-block">
                            **نيوزيلندا** <br>
                            <small class="text-muted">Monday 8:00 a.m. to Saturday 11:59 a.m.</small>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="col-4">Wellington</td>
                    <td class="col-4 text-start">**+64 800 170 166** (Toll Free)</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <footer class="text-center py-3 mt-4 text-muted">
            <p>جميع الأوقات بتوقيت المنطقة المحلية.</p>
        </footer>

    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>